Job Responsibilities

  Work with business stakeholders, Project Managers and SMEs to Identify, propose, prioritize and implement test plans and test automations
  Work closely with stakeholders and SMEs to understand business requirements
  Create test scenarios and test cases
  Create test data
  Ensure test cases are executed in accordance to priority assigned
  Conduct functional testing and user acceptance testing

Experiance:&nbsp;

  Degree or Diploma in Computer Science, Software Engineering or other equivalent degrees/experience
  At least 2 years’ experience in an Test/QA Engineer role
  Familiar with or have experience with testing tools and writing scripts in test automation
